-- Rwanda's Power, Water Utility Returns to Profit in 2009, New Times Says
-- B y   D a v i d   M a l i n g h a   D o y a
-- 2010-10-25T05:47:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/rwanda-s-power-water-utility-returns-to-profit-in-2009-new-times-says.html
Rwanda’s electricity and water
utility’s profit was about 300 million Rwandan francs ($508,000)
in 2009, New Times reported, citing Managing Director Yves
Muyange.  Rwanda Electricity Corp. & Rwanda Water and Sanitation
Corporation moved from losses after restructuring the company,
the Kigali-based newspaper today cited Muyange as saying. It
planned to increase the proportion of households with
electricity to 16 percent from 9 percent within five years, New
Times said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
